{
  "video_id": "QO7oN1G5Qgg",
  "title": "California law: stop the government from forfeiting your property",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6700.0,
      "end_time": 9120.0,
      "text": "Once the government has actually seized your property,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 9120.0,
      "end_time": 11299.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s many defenses that you can use."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11300.0,
      "end_time": 14100.0,
      "text": "Number one are going to be procedural grounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14100.0,
      "end_time": 16720.0,
      "text": "Congress and our State legislatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16720.0,
      "end_time": 19840.0,
      "text": "have put into place certain procedures"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19840.0,
      "end_time": 22330.0,
      "text": "that the government must follow in order"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22330.0,
      "end_time": 25279.0,
      "text": "to properly forfeit property that has been"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25280.0,
      "end_time": 27190.0,
      "text": "seized from private citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27190.0,
      "end_time": 30110.0,
      "text": "Now, there is a difference between a seizure"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30110.0,
      "end_time": 31370.0,
      "text": "and a forfeiture."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31370.0,
      "end_time": 35540.0,
      "text": "The seizure is related to the actual taking of the property."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35540.0,
      "end_time": 38180.0,
      "text": "But it doesn&#39;t go to show whether or not"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38180.0,
      "end_time": 40180.0,
      "text": "the government can keep it."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40180.0,
      "end_time": 44660.0,
      "text": "So the forfeiture is a process of which the government proves"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44660.0,
      "end_time": 47449.0,
      "text": "that not only did they lawfully seize something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47450.0,
      "end_time": 51450.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re lawfully entitled to keep that seized property."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51450.0,
      "end_time": 52990.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where we come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52990.0,
      "end_time": 55330.0,
      "text": "Congress has put in procedures to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55330.0,
      "end_time": 57420.0,
      "text": "that your rights aren&#39;t being violated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57420.0,
      "end_time": 59360.0,
      "text": "both in the seizure and the forfeiture."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59360.0,
      "end_time": 63890.0,
      "text": "The government must follow specific procedures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63900.0,
      "end_time": 68180.0,
      "text": "including filings of complaints and notice requirements."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68180.0,
      "end_time": 71400.0,
      "text": "If they fail to do these things, then the person"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71400.0,
      "end_time": 73660.0,
      "text": "that they actually seized the property from"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73660.0,
      "end_time": 77119.0,
      "text": "has a grounds to get the property back."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77120.0,
      "end_time": 79600.0,
      "text": "An experienced asset forfeiture attorney"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79600.0,
      "end_time": 81880.0,
      "text": "will be able to look at the facts"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81880.0,
      "end_time": 86229.0,
      "text": "and challenge the procedures in which the authorities have"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86230.0,
      "end_time": 88630.0,
      "text": "actually seized and are attempting"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88630.0,
      "end_time": 91750.0,
      "text": "to forfeit your property."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91750.0,
      "end_time": 93960.0,
      "text": "In addition to those procedural grounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93960.0,
      "end_time": 97179.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to have various defenses that you can use."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97180.0,
      "end_time": 100930.0,
      "text": "These offenses include the innocent owner defense."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100930.0,
      "end_time": 103920.0,
      "text": "This defense rests upon the premise"
