      "text": "used for illegal activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109960.0,
      "end_time": 113290.0,
      "text": "Or as a recipient of these funds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113300.0,
      "end_time": 116290.0,
      "text": "you didn&#39;t realize they were coming from illicit sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116290.0,
      "end_time": 120700.0,
      "text": "For instance, what if you are a property owner."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120700.0,
